                            <comment id="14092053" author="remkop@yahoo.com" created="Sun, 10 Aug 2014 08:22:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Interestingly, this does not happen if the pattern has only one &apos;{&apos; character, like &lt;tt&gt;&amp;lt;PatternLayout pattern=&quot;%d{HH:mm:ss.SSS  - %msg%n&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;/tt&gt;: in this case the application will not hang. The app hangs only when the pattern has two or more opening  &apos;{&apos; characters but not enough closing  &apos;}&apos; characters.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
